<section id="anatomie">
<div class="container">
  <div class="section-label">01 — Anatomie van de hartkleppen</div>
  <h2>Vier kleppen, één pomp.</h2>

  <div class="heart-diagram">
    <div>
      <p>Het hart is een dubbele pomp met twee gescheiden circulaties. In elke helft zitten twee kleppen die samen éénrichtingsstroom garanderen: bloed kan alleen vooruit, nooit terug.</p>
      <p>De kleppen bestaan uit dunne, flexibele <strong>slippen (cusps of leaflets)</strong>, opgehangen aan een fibreuze ring: de <strong>anulus</strong>. Ze openen en sluiten volledig passief — aangedreven door drukgradiënten, niet door spiercontractie.</p>

      <div class="pull-quote">Hartkleppen zijn passieve structuren. Ze openen wanneer de druk vóór hen hoger is dan erachter, en sluiten zodra dit omkeert.</div>

      <p>Structureel worden de kleppen in twee types verdeeld:</p>
      <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 1.2rem; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.9; color:var(--text-muted);">
        <li><strong>Atrioventriculaire (AV) kleppen</strong> — mitraal- en tricuspidaalklep — liggen tussen atrium en ventrikel en worden gefixeerd door chordae tendineae en papillairspieren om prolaps te voorkomen.</li>
        <li><strong>Semilunaire kleppen</strong> — aorta- en pulmonaalklep — liggen aan de uitstroom van de ventrikels en hebben geen chordae; ze sluiten door de druk van het bloed dat terugstroomt.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <!-- SVG schematische hartdoorsnede -->
      <div class="heart-svg-wrap">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 360 380" width="340" height="360" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" font-family="'JetBrains Mono', monospace">
          <!-- Achtergrond -->
          <rect width="360" height="380" fill="#0D1B2A" rx="8"/>

          <!-- Labels boven -->
          <text x="85" y="20" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" letter-spacing="1">RECHTS</text>
          <text x="275" y="20" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" letter-spacing="1">LINKS</text>
          <line x1="180" y1="10" x2="180" y2="370" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>

          <!-- Rechter atrium -->
          <ellipse cx="90" cy="100" rx="65" ry="55" fill="#1B3A5C" stroke="#2C6FAC" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <text x="90" y="97" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" font-size="8.5" text-anchor="middle">Rechter</text>
          <text x="90" y="110" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" font-size="8.5" text-anchor="middle">Atrium</text>

          <!-- Linker atrium -->
          <ellipse cx="270" cy="100" rx="65" ry="55" fill="#4A1515" stroke="#C0392B" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <text x="270" y="97" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" font-size="8.5" text-anchor="middle">Linker</text>
          <text x="270" y="110" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" font-size="8.5" text-anchor="middle">Atrium</text>

          <!-- Rechter ventrikel -->
          <path d="M 30 175 Q 30 330 105 345 Q 150 355 160 280 Q 165 220 160 175 Z" fill="#1B3A5C" stroke="#2C6FAC" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <text x="90" y="270" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" font-size="8.5" text-anchor="middle">Rechter</text>
          <text x="90" y="283" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" font-size="8.5" text-anchor="middle">Ventrikel</text>

          <!-- Linker ventrikel (dikker septum) -->
          <path d="M 200 175 Q 195 220 200 280 Q 210 355 255 345 Q 330 330 330 175 Z" fill="#4A1515" stroke="#C0392B" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="270" y="270" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" font-size="8.5" text-anchor="middle">Linker</text>
          <text x="270" y="283" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" font-size="8.5" text-anchor="middle">Ventrikel</text>

          <!-- Septum -->
          <line x1="160" y1="170" x2="200" y2="170" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="158" y1="282" x2="202" y2="282" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)" stroke-width="2"/>

          <!-- TRICUSPIDAALKLEP -->
          <ellipse cx="132" cy="172" rx="22" ry="8" fill="#6B3FA0" stroke="#9B6DCA" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="58" y="168" fill="#9B6DCA" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">Tricuspidaal</text>
          <line x1="80" y1="168" x2="110" y2="170" stroke="#6B3FA0" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2,2"/>

          <!-- MITRAALKLEP -->
          <ellipse cx="228" cy="172" rx="20" ry="7" fill="#0E6B7C" stroke="#1A8FA3" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="305" y="162" fill="#1A8FA3" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">Mitraal</text>
          <line x1="248" y1="169" x2="290" y2="163" stroke="#0E6B7C" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2,2"/>

          <!-- PULMONAALKLEP (uitstroom rechts bovenin) -->
          <path d="M 50 130 Q 60 110 80 105 Q 95 125 80 145 Z" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <ellipse cx="88" cy="148" rx="18" ry="6" fill="#2D6A4F" stroke="#52B788" stroke-width="2" transform="rotate(-30,88,148)"/>
          <text x="30" y="140" fill="#52B788" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle">Pulmonaal</text>

          <!-- Pulmonaalarterie -->
          <path d="M 80 130 Q 75 80 110 60" stroke="#52B788" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
          <text x="75" y="55" fill="#52B788" font-size="7.5" text-anchor="middle">A. pulmonalis</text>

          <!-- AORTAKLEP (uitstroom links bovenin) — HIGHLIGHT -->
          <ellipse cx="238" cy="148" rx="20" ry="7" fill="#9B1C1C" stroke="#E74C3C" stroke-width="2.5" transform="rotate(20,238,148)"/>
          <!-- Glow effect aortaklep -->
          <ellipse cx="238" cy="148" rx="26" ry="11" fill="none" stroke="#E74C3C" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" transform="rotate(20,238,148)"/>
          <text x="318" y="135" fill="#E74C3C" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold">Aortaklep ★</text>
          <line x1="292" y1="137" x2="258" y2="143" stroke="#9B1C1C" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2,2"/>

          <!-- Aorta -->
          <path d="M 258 130 Q 275 70 290 50 Q 310 30 330 40" stroke="#C0392B" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
          <text x="315" y="45" fill="#C0392B" font-size="7.5" text-anchor="middle">Aorta</text>

          <!-- Vena cava superior (rechts) -->
          <line x1="55" y1="45" x2="70" y2="68" stroke="#2C6FAC" stroke-width="2"/>
          <text x="40" y="40" fill="#2C6FAC" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">V. cava sup.</text>

          <!-- Longvenen (links) -->
          <line x1="310" y1="65" x2="300" y2="88" stroke="#C0392B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="2,2"/>
          <text x="328" y="60" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.35)" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle">Longvenen</text>

          <!-- Stroomrichtingspijlen -->
          <!-- Rechts: blauw (veneus) -->
          <path d="M 90 153 L 90 168" stroke="#4A90D9" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arr-blue)"/>
          <path d="M 88 175 L 88 200" stroke="#4A90D9" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arr-blue)"/>

          <!-- Links: rood (arterieel) -->
          <path d="M 228 153 L 228 168" stroke="#C0392B" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arr-red)"/>
          <path d="M 226 175 L 226 200" stroke="#C0392B" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arr-red)"/>

          <defs>
            <marker id="arr-blue" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="3" refY="3" orient="auto">
              <path d="M0,0 L6,3 L0,6 Z" fill="#4A90D9"/>
            </marker>
            <marker id="arr-red" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="3" refY="3" orient="auto">
              <path d="M0,0 L6,3 L0,6 Z" fill="#C0392B"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>

          <!-- Legenda -->
          <rect x="10" y="345" width="8" height="8" fill="#4A90D9" rx="1"/>
          <text x="22" y="353" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" font-size="7.5">Veneus (O₂-arm)</text>
          <rect x="120" y="345" width="8" height="8" fill="#C0392B" rx="1"/>
          <text x="132" y="353" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" font-size="7.5">Arterieel (O₂-rijk)</text>
          <rect x="240" y="345" width="8" height="8" fill="#E74C3C" rx="1"/>
          <text x="252" y="353" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" font-size="7.5">Aortaklep (focus)</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="valve-grid">
    <div class="valve-card aorta">
      <div class="valve-name">Aortaklep</div>
      <div class="valve-type">Semilunair · Links · 3 cusps</div>
      <p>Ligt tussen linker ventrikel en aorta ascendens. Drie gelijke cusps (left, right, non-coronary). Direct boven de klep ontspringen de linker- en rechtercoronairarterie uit de sinus van Valsalva. Normaal klepoppervlak: <strong>2,5–3,5 cm²</strong>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="valve-card mitraal">
      <div class="valve-name">Mitraalklep</div>
      <div class="valve-type">Atrioventriculair · Links · 2 cusps</div>
      <p>Tussen linker atrium en linker ventrikel. Twee cusps (anterior en posterior) gefixeerd door chordae tendineae aan twee papillairspieren. De ingewikkeldste klep om chirurgisch te repareren.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="valve-card pulmonaal">
      <div class="valve-name">Pulmonaalklep</div>
      <div class="valve-type">Semilunair · Rechts · 3 cusps</div>
      <p>Tussen rechter ventrikel en arteria pulmonalis. Werkt hetzelfde als de aortaklep maar onder veel lagere drukken (systolisch ~25 mmHg). Wordt zelden chirurgisch vervangen bij volwassenen.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="valve-card tricuspidaal">
      <div class="valve-name">Tricuspidaalklep</div>
      <div class="valve-type">Atrioventriculair · Rechts · 3 cusps</div>
      <p>Tussen rechter atrium en rechter ventrikel. Drie cusps en drie papillairspieren. Pathologie hier is vaak secundair aan linkerhartziekten (verhoogde drukken). Correctie soms gelijktijdig met aortaklepoperatie.</p>
